name: android-release-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for release and deployment of Android apps
globs: **/*.{kt,java,gradle.kts}

- Implement proper versioning (semantic versioning)
- Use proper signing configuration
- Implement proper release notes
- Use Play Store features (in-app updates, app bundle)
- Implement proper feature flagging
- Set up proper release pipeline
- Implement A/B testing when necessary
- Use Firebase App Distribution for pre-releases
- Implement proper analytics event tracking
- Set up crash reporting (Firebase Crashlytics)
- Implement proper user feedback channels
- Use phased rollouts for major updates 